    <item>
      <title>美国生产者价格上涨，可能给美联储青睐的指标带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/prices-paid-to-us-producers-picked-up-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十月份美国生产者价格有所回升，部分原因是投资组合管理和其他类别价格上涨，这些价格是美联储优先考虑的通胀指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/prices-paid-to-us-producers-picked-up-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场动荡 中国铜买家大幅削减年度合约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/china-s-copper-buyers-slash-annual-contracts-with-market-in-flux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的铜进口商正在通过年度供应谈判（曾是全球金属市场的风向标）控制购买的铜数量，并选择现货供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/china-s-copper-buyers-slash-annual-contracts-with-market-in-flux</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行行长任期不明朗影响降息希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/no-clarity-on-rbi-governor-s-term-weighs-on-rate-cut-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长任期还有不到一个月就到期，其未来前景不明朗，这给利率预期增添了另一层复杂性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/no-clarity-on-rbi-governor-s-term-weighs-on-rate-cut-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tapestry 正在回购为收购 Capri 而发行的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/tapestry-is-buying-back-its-bonds-issued-to-fund-capri-purchase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tapestry Inc. 计划回购其为收购 Capri Holdings 而出售的价值 61 亿美元的债券，此前该公司因反垄断压力而放弃了这笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/tapestry-is-buying-back-its-bonds-issued-to-fund-capri-purchase</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国法官裁定伦敦资本与金融公司老板实施庞氏骗局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/london-capital-finance-bosses-ran-a-ponzi-scheme-uk-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦一名法官裁定，伦敦资本与金融有限公司 (London Capital &amp; Finance Plc) 的老板实施庞氏骗局，从散户投资者手中收取数亿英镑，并将其中大部分花在自己身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/london-capital-finance-bosses-ran-a-ponzi-scheme-uk-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库格勒称美联储必须同时关注通胀和就业目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kugler-says-fed-must-focus-on-both-inflation-and-jobs-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事阿德里安娜·库格勒表示，政策制定者必须同时关注央行的通胀和就业目标，并指出劳动力市场正在降温，实现美联储 2% 通胀目标的进展放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kugler-says-fed-must-focus-on-both-inflation-and-jobs-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科威特考虑更换 1 万亿美元财富基金负责人 KIA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kuwait-is-said-to-weigh-replacing-md-of-1-trillion-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科威特 1 万亿美元财富基金的董事总经理在任职三年后即将离职，这也结束了这家全球投资者动荡的任期，近年来，其光芒一直被地区同行所掩盖，因为这些同行近年来做出了更为耀眼的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kuwait-is-said-to-weigh-replacing-md-of-1-trillion-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PPI 利率之争悬而未决，美国期货价格波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生产者价格通胀指标符合预期后，美国股指期货趋于稳定，而投资者对 12 月份降息的可能性存在争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍楚尔计划恢复纽约市拥堵收费制度，收费 9 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/hochul-plans-to-revive-nyc-congestion-pricing-plan-with-9-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州长凯西·霍楚尔计划恢复对进入曼哈顿大部分地区的司机征收拥堵费。几个月前，她突然在原定实施日期前取消了这项 15 美元的收费，理由是这项收费会给工薪家庭和小企业带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/hochul-plans-to-revive-nyc-congestion-pricing-plan-with-9-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
